description: BENTEN BOWL serves up fast, clean, and healthy Japanese cuisine.  All sauces are made from scratch and contain zero MSG or artificial ingredients.This truck is absolutely ideal for office lunches, school events, and parties. You must try their delicious original Salmon Poke, Teriyaki, and cold dessert “Coffee Jelly with Himalayan Salt Cream”. Vegan, Vegetarian, and Gluten Free menus are also available.
name: Benten Bowl
